# ── Fee Config (do not change — baked into smart contract) ────────────────────
# Platform trading fee: 0.05% (5 bps) — hardcoded in buy_option.rs / sell_option.rs
# Settlement fee ITM:   0.05% of payoff, capped at 50 USDC
# Settlement fee OTM:   0%
